author: 𝓕𝓵𝔂 𝓨𝓸𝓾𝓷𝓰𝓲𝓷
text: "Change your thoughts. Change your words. Change your actions. Change your direction. Change your priorities. Change your life.

author: 𝓕𝓵𝔂 𝓨𝓸𝓾𝓷𝓰𝓲𝓷
text: "The way you treat yourself sets the standard for others."

author: 𝓕𝓵𝔂 𝓨𝓸𝓾𝓷𝓰𝓲𝓷
text: She Just Want Some Love An Affection 🥷❤️
